# Layout Rules

## Source of Truth
agent-os/product/tech-stack.md defines all stack decisions.

## Fonts
Use next/font/google
- Space Grotesk: weights 400, 500, 600, 700 — variable: --font-display
- Inter: weights 400, 500 — variable: --font-body
Apply both variables to <html> element as className

## Theme
- Use ThemeProvider from next-themes
- attribute="class"
- defaultTheme="dark"
- enableSystem=false
- Wrap entire app

## Body Classes
- font-body (maps to Inter via Tailwind)
- antialiased
- bg-[var(--bg-primary)]
- text-[var(--text-primary)]
- transition-colors duration-300

## Metadata
- title: "Sam Dhanalakota — Senior Full-Stack Engineer"
- description: "Senior Full-Stack Engineer building enterprise 
  platforms at scale. React, TypeScript, Node.js, AWS. 
  Based in Vancouver, BC."

## Rules
- No hardcoded colors
- ThemeProvider must be outermost wrapper inside <body>
- fonts applied to <html> not <body>
